    <item>
      <title>摩根士丹利的威尔逊认为股市几乎没有熊市迹象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/morgan-stanley-s-wilson-sees-few-signs-of-bear-market-in-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利的迈克·威尔逊表示，尽管季节性因素不佳和增长前景不明朗可能会限制美国股市在本季度剩余时间内的涨幅，但股市全面崩溃的可能性很小。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/morgan-stanley-s-wilson-sees-few-signs-of-bear-market-in-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 17:00:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛和摩根大通称市场预期经济衰退的可能性上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/goldman-jpmorgan-say-markets-pricing-in-higher-recession-odds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周，市场动荡一度引发华尔街恐慌，此后金融市场发出警告称，经济衰退即将来临的可能性更高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/goldman-jpmorgan-say-markets-pricing-in-higher-recession-odds</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 16:57:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
